post.content:
Hi Everyone,

We just found out that we can have a table to sell fruit at this Saturday’s Health Expo. It runs from 8 to 12. We really need a few volunteers to man the table. If you can help please contact Susie at 440-877-1299 or susielbp@juno.com.

Thanks!

Susie Perez and Karen Svoboda
Fruit Sale Chairs
